courses.customDesc:
Any Animal Science Course can go here.

Select one course from: ASCI221, ASCI222, ASCI223, ASCI224, ASCI225; DSCI230.

courses.subject: Choose One
courses.customDesc: Choose one of the following: BIO111, or BIO161.

courses.subject: GE
courses.customDesc: One course from each of the following GE areas must be completed: A1, A2, A3, C1, C2, Lower-Division C Elective, Upper-Division C, D1, Lower-Division E, and F. Upper-Division C should be taken only after Junior standing is reached (90 units). Refer to online catalog for GE course selection, United States Cultural Pluralism (USCP) and Graduation Writing Requirement (GWR) requirements.
